title: What jungler to play
body: I want to start playing a new jungler but im not sure who to play. I want someone who can be strong by himself and not rely too heavily on others. I'm lvl 7 {{champion:24}} and i quite like the style of him and i played {{champion:12}} in the jungle for a while and got really good at him but im not sure who to play now. Also i dont care if the champ is usually in another lane

replies.body: i actually didnt know ren could jg. Also didnt know naut could jg.

Naut always could. Much like Maokai and stuff, its old school tank jungler style. Renekton Jungle isn't traditional, but there was an NA Renekton one trick  (Uncle Jamal) who started doing it like 2 seasons ago and its not bad. Take W level 1 for an easier clear.
